                    "description": "Deterministic turn lifecycle phase (RULES.md §4). Each turn executes all 8 phases in order: StartTurn → DeploymentPhase → AttackPhase → AttackResolution → CleanupPhase → ReinforcementPhase → DrawPhase → EndTurn. Player actions are only valid in specific phases.",
